{
  "verses": [
    {
      "verse_num": 1,
      "segments": [
        {
          "type": "narrative",
          "text": "And he looked up, and saw the rich men casting their gifts into the treasury."
        }
      ],
      "footnotes": [],
      "references": [],
      "heading": []
    },
    {
      "verse_num": 2,
      "segments": [
        {
          "type": "narrative",
          "text": "And he saw also a certain poor widow casting in thither two mites."
        }
      ],
      "footnotes": [],
      "references": [],
      "heading": []
    },
    {
      "verse_num": 3,
      "segments": [
        {
          "type": "narrative",
          "text": "And he said,"
        }
      ],
      "footnotes": [],
      "references": [],
      "heading": []
    },
    {
      "verse_num": 5,
      "segments": [
        {
          "type": "narrative",
          "text": "And as some spake of the temple, how it was adorned with goodly stones and gifts,"
        },
        {
          "type": "speech",
          "text": "he said,",
          "speaker": "Jesus"
        }
      ],
      "footnotes": [],
      "references": [],
      "heading": [
        "The Temple and Future Events"
      ]
    },
    {
      "verse_num": 7,
      "segments": [
        {
          "type": "speech",
          "text": "Master, but when shall these things be? and what sign will there be when these things shall come to pass?",
          "speaker": "Disciples"
        }
      ],
      "footnotes": [],
      "references": [],
      "heading": []
    },
    {
      "verse_num": 8,
      "segments": [
        {
          "type": "narrative",
          "text": "And he said,"
        }
      ],
      "footnotes": [],
      "references": [],
      "heading": []
    },
    {
      "verse_num": 10,
      "segments": [
        {
          "type": "narrative",
          "text": "Then said he unto them,"
        }
      ],
      "footnotes": [],
      "references": [],
      "heading": []
    },
    {
      "verse_num": 29,
      "segments": [
        {
          "type": "narrative",
          "text": "And he spake to them a parable;"
        }
      ],
      "footnotes": [],
      "references": [],
      "heading": []
    },
    {
      "verse_num": 37,
      "segments": [
        {
          "type": "narrative",
          "text": "And in the day time he was teaching in the temple; and at night he went out, and abode in the mount that is called the mount of Olives."
        }
      ],
      "footnotes": [],
      "references": [],
      "heading": []
    },
    {
      "verse_num": 38,
      "segments": [
        {
          "type": "narrative",
          "text": "And all the people came early in the morning to him in the temple, for to hear him."
        }
      ],
      "footnotes": [],
      "references": [],
      "heading": []
    }
  ]
}